cription}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Russia}}\n| 1993\n| 1\n| Victims of the [[1993 Russian constitutional crisis|1993 Russian coup attempt]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=\u0423\u043a\u0430\u0437 \u041f\u0440\u0435\u0437\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0430 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0439\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0424\u0435\u0434\u0435\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u043e\u0442 06.10.1993 \u0433. \u2116 1589 |url=http://kremlin.ru/acts/bank/4549 |website=\u041f\u0440\u0435\u0437\u0438\u0434\u0435\u043d\u0442 \u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u0438 |language=ru}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}\n| 1994\n| 1\n| Victims of the [[Markale massacres]]\n|<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kifner |first1=John |title=Terror in Sarajevo; Sarajevans Mourn and Rage While Life and Death Go On |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/07/world/terror-in-sarajevo-sarajevans-mourn-and-rage-while-life-and-death-go-on.html |website=The New York Times |date=February 7, 1994}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Belgium}}\n| 1994\n| 1\n| The killing of 10 Belgian soldiers during the [[Rwandan Civil War]]\n| <ref name=\"Belgium1\">{{cite web|title=When is a National Day of Mourning held?|date=March 16, 2012|website=vrt.be|url=https://www.vrt.be/vrtnws/en/2012/03/16/when_is_a_nationaldayofmourningheld-1-1246829/}}</ref><ref name=\"Belgium2\">{{cite web|title=OVERZICHT. Dagen van nationale rouw in het verleden|url=https://www.gva.be/cnt/dmf20160323_02198293/wat-betekenen-drie-dagen-van-nationale-rouw|date=March 23, 2016|author=Eigen Berichtgeving|language=be|website=Gazet Van Antwerpen}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|United States}}\n| 1994\n| 1\n| [[Death and state funeral of Richard Nixon|Death]] of former U.S. President [[Richard Nixon]]\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Apple Jr |first1=R. W. |title=The 37th President: The Overview; Tributes to Nixon Underline Triumphs, Not the Downfall |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1994/04/24/us/37th-president-overview-tributes-nixon-underline-triumphs-not-downfall.html |website=The New York Tim