r\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u7e41\u661f)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"July\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u67d2\u6708)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Jiayou Jiayou\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u52a0\u6cb9\u52a0\u6cb9)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Rhythm evolution\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u97f3\u5f8b\u8fdb\u5316)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Zao Meng Wang Guo\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u9020\u68a6\u738b\u56fd)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Unfinished sketch\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u672a\u5b8c\u6210\u7684\u7d20\u63cf)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Ai Qing Jing Wei Xian\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u7231\u60c5\u7ecf\u7eac\u7ebf)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Bei Dui Zhe Xiang Nian\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u80cc\u5bf9\u7740\u60f3\u5ff5)\n| rowspan=\"10\" | 2017\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"RunForMe\"\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"War\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u6218)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Red Light, Green Light\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: 123\u6728\u5934\u4eba)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Happy Rotation\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u5feb\u4e50\u5faa\u73af)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Adventure Times\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u5192\u9669\u65f6\u4ee3)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Ji Ming Yue\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u5bc4\u660e\u6708)\n| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''SING''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Ru Meng Ling\" ([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u5982\u68a6\u4ee4)\n| \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | \"Like This\"\n| \u2014\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{N/A|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"