ers|simplified chinese]]: \u671b\u6708)\n|\u2014\n| {{N/A|Non-album single}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | \"Hua Qiang\"([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u82b1\u67aa)\n|\u2014\n| {{N/A|Non-album single}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" | \"Hello, Imperial Palaces in Beijing\"([[Pinyin|Pinyin]]: gu gong ni hao ma)([[Simplified Chinese characters|simplified chinese]]: \u6545\u5bab\u4f60\u597d\u5417)\n|\u2014\n| {{N/A|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"4\" | <sup>1</sup><small>Initial released as \"The girl who crossed space-time\" ({{zh|\u7a7f\u8d8a\u53e4\u4ee3\u7684\u5c11\u5973}})</small><br><sup>2</sup><small>Lai Meiyun's voice is on longer featured in singles released after 2017</small>\n|}\n\n==Accolades==\n===[[Ku Music Asian Music Awards]]===\n{{awards table|style=text-align:center}}\n|-\n| 2018\n| S.I.N.G (SING Girls)\n| Rising Popularity Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n===[[Tencent]] Streaming Award===\n{{awards table|style=text-align:center}}\n|-\n| 2018\n| S.I.N.G (SING Girls)\n| 2017 Rising Popularity Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n===China Asia Musia Festival (AMF)===\n{{awards table|style=text-align:center}}\n|-\n| 2019\n| S.I.N.G (SING Girls)\n| 2019 Rising Popularity Award\n| {{won}}\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Films ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Title\n!Notes\n|-\n|2017\n|[[Our Shining Days]]\n|As S.I.N.G members\n|}\n\n== Product Endorsements ==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Year\n!Project\n!Product\n|-\n|2016\n|Online Game\n|Zhu Zai Xi You ([[simplified chinese]]: \u4e3b\u5bb0\u897f\u6e38) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://passport.weibo.com/visitor/visitor?entry=miniblog&a=enter&url=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F5281360151%2FDqWaCBGIo%3Ftype%3Dcomment&domain=.weibo.com&ua=php-sso_sdk_client-0.6.28&_rand=1549555222.0763|title=SING\u5973\u56e2\u4ee3\u8a003D\u6697\u9ed1MMOARPG\u7f51\u9875\u6e38\u620f|website=passport.weibo.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|2018\n|Mobile Game\n|Ark Order ([[simplified chinese]]: \u65b9\u821f\u6307\u4ee